title: Agnieszka Radwanska marches on at Tianjin Open
text:
Agnieszka Radwanska marches on at Tianjin Open 15 Oct 2015 14:17:01 
comments 
Second seed Agnieszka Radwanska eased into the quarter-finals of the Tianjin Open. 
The Pole, who has still to secure her place at the end-of-season WTA Finals in Singapore, defeated local hope Wang Qiang 6-1 6-1. 
Next up for Radwanska is a clash with Russian teenage Elizaveta Kulichkova, who saw off countrywoman Evgeniya Rodina 6-2 7-5. 
Lyudmyla Kichenok was unable to follow up her first-round upset of US Open champion Flavia Pennetta, going down 6-7 (5/7) 6-2 6-4 to Chinese wild card Duan Ying-Ying, who next meets Danka Kovinic. Related Sport News
